<inglise> Article 6 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 6 </eesti>
<inglise> 1. </inglise>
<eesti> 1. </eesti>
<inglise> A committee on the adaptation to technical progress of the Directives on the removal of technical barriers to trade in electrical equipment for use in potentially explosive atmospheres, hereinafter called "the committee", is hereby set up; it shall be composed of representatives of the Member States under the chairmanship of a representative of the Commission. </inglise>
