<eesti> Artikkel 7 </eesti>
<inglise> 1. </inglise>
<eesti> 1. </eesti>
<inglise> If recourse is had to the procedure defined in this Article, the matter shall be placed before the committee by its chairman, on his own initiative or at the request of the representative of a Member State. </inglise>
