<inglise> At least 41 votes in favour shall be required before it can deliver its opinion, the votes of the Member States being weighted as provided in Article 148 (2) of the Treaty. </inglise>
<eesti> Arvamuseesitamiseks on vaja v&auml;hemalt 41 poolth&auml;&auml;lt, liikmesriikide h&auml;&auml;li arvestatakse asutamislepingu artikli 148 l&otilde;ikes 2 s&auml;testatud korras. </eesti>
